# Keep the build context small and avoid leaking host state into the image.
# (Source is bind-mounted at runtime for dev, so it need not be in the context.)
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/out
**/build
**/.turbo
**/coverage
.git
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
**/*.tsbuildinfo
supabase/.branches
supabase/.temp
notes
assets
